title: Mountain Tomb of Pain
story: For centuries the tomb was considered lost. These days it is badly infested by ants. It is said that countless treasures of ancient books can be found here.

notes.text: A mouth-shaped ironbound door with two keyholes to the north.
Candles among rubble on the ground.
A key at the bottom of a pool.
A stuffed gnome hunter with a key in their hands.
Some gold, an enchanted mace and a chainmail tucked under some debris.
